  "text": "These cystic tumors are divided into two categories (serous and mucinous), and within the serous forms there are five subcategories [CITATION_1] . The serous solid adenoma is the rarest entity of these five subcategories. The first case was described in 1996 by Perez-Ordonez et al. [CITATION_2] .",
